Revision history for Perl extension XML::Filter::XML_Directory_Pruner.

1.2  Fri Jul 05 2002

     - Added package method __PACKAGE__->mtype()

     - Updated $pkg->debug() to accept arguments > 1

     - Updated $pkg->exclude and $pkg->include to accept multiple 'matching' criteria (is backwards compatible)

     - Updated POD

1.1  Tue Jul 02 2002

     - Added $pkg->on_enter_start_element()

     - Added $pkg->on_exit_end_element()

     - Added $pkg->current_level()

     - Added $pkg->skip_level()

     - Fixed a typo in test.pl

     - Updated POD

1.0  Thu May 04 2002

     - original version.

